# Vercel deploy: ship ONLY the static landing site + build inputs.
# The repo root is a monorepo with 20MB+ of marketing videos and
# screenshots that must not be uploaded (hits the 10MB deploy limit).

# Ignore everything at the repo root
/*

# Re-include the static site (outputDirectory) and its contents
!/site/

# Re-include the install script (buildCommand copies it into site/)
!/scripts/

# Re-include the Vercel config itself
!/vercel.json
